1
00:00:08,310 --> 00:00:11,650
<font color="yellow">Were Soo Yeon and I this close?</font>

2
00:00:11,650 --> 00:00:13,240
<font color="yellow">I'm marrying Soo Yeon.</font>

3
00:00:13,240 --> 00:00:16,080
<font color="yellow">Let me ask one thing. What's the relationship between...</font>

4
00:00:16,080 --> 00:00:17,110
<font color="yellow">Lawyer Oh and me?</font>

5
00:00:17,110 --> 00:00:18,830
<font color="yellow">If you can eliminate Gi Tan,</font>

6
00:00:18,830 --> 00:00:20,680
<font color="yellow">I'm willing to team up with you again.</font>

7
00:00:20,680 --> 00:00:22,310
<font color="yellow">Who are you?</font>

8
00:00:22,750 --> 00:00:24,950
<font color="yellow">You are not my son.</font>

9
00:00:24,950 --> 00:00:27,580
<font color="yellow">How long will you hide that he has dementia?</font>

10
00:00:27,580 --> 00:00:29,670
<font color="yellow">We're currently editing his will.</font>

11
00:00:29,670 --> 00:00:32,080
<font color="yellow">After we're done, I'll send him off to a care centre.</font>

12
00:00:32,080 --> 00:00:34,170
<font color="yellow">I found evidence of Il Jae's corruption.</font>

13
00:00:34,170 --> 00:00:35,180
<font color="yellow">Who are you?</font>

14
00:00:35,180 --> 00:00:37,120
<font color="yellow">This must be Il Jae's doing.</font>

15
00:00:37,120 --> 00:00:38,280
<font color="yellow">I'll report to the police.</font>

16
00:00:38,280 --> 00:00:41,290
<font color="yellow">His necklace and mine are the same.</font>

17
00:00:41,290 --> 00:00:43,270
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon, where are you?</font>

18
00:00:43,270 --> 00:00:44,760
<font color="yellow">Have you regained your memory?</font>

19
00:00:44,760 --> 00:00:47,010
<font color="yellow">But you're a month too late.</font>

20
00:00:47,010 --> 00:00:49,940
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon is completely mine.</font>

21
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:51,930
<font color="yellow">That's what happened.</font>

22
00:00:51,930 --> 00:00:53,280
<font color="yellow">Give up on Soo Yeon.</font>

23
00:00:53,850 --> 00:00:55,350
<font color="yellow">I won this.</font>

24
00:00:58,880 --> 00:01:00,050
<font color="yellow">Did I ever...</font>

25
00:01:00,550 --> 00:01:02,280
<font color="yellow">make your heart flutter?</font>

26
00:01:02,280 --> 00:01:03,310
<font color="yellow">Did I ever...</font>

27
00:01:03,780 --> 00:01:05,510
<font color="yellow">make your heart pound?</font>

28
00:01:26,080 --> 00:01:28,740
<font color="yellow">It doesn't look like you feel the same way.</font>

29
00:01:28,740 --> 00:01:30,680
<font color="yellow">- Gun Woo.
-  Don't say anything, Soo Yeon.</font>

30
00:01:31,310 --> 00:01:32,850
<font color="yellow">I don't want to hear anything...</font>

31
00:01:34,150 --> 00:01:35,550
<font color="yellow">unless you're saying, "I love you."</font>

32
00:01:41,010 --> 00:01:42,050
<font color="yellow">You can take your time.</font>

33
00:01:43,310 --> 00:01:44,850
<font color="yellow">Take as much time as you need.</font>

34
00:01:47,380 --> 00:01:48,550
<font color="yellow">It's okay.</font>

35
00:01:57,410 --> 00:01:58,410
<font color="yellow">Chairman.</font>

36
00:01:59,310 --> 00:02:01,110
<font color="yellow">Chairman, what's wrong?</font>

37
00:02:02,850 --> 00:02:05,750
<font color="yellow">Who knows everything about Soo Yeon and my history?</font>

38
00:02:07,150 --> 00:02:10,190
<font color="yellow">I believe Chae Ryung knows everything.</font>

39
00:02:10,190 --> 00:02:11,460
<font color="yellow">Where is she?</font>

40
00:02:11,460 --> 00:02:13,180
<font color="yellow">I heard she's in China but...</font>

41
00:02:13,980 --> 00:02:15,580
<font color="yellow">Get my plane ready.</font>

42
00:02:16,780 --> 00:02:18,650
<font color="yellow">- Pardon?
-  I need to find out...</font>

43
00:02:19,380 --> 00:02:20,880
<font color="yellow">the history between...</font>

44
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:24,180
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon and me.</font>

45
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,880
<font color="yellow">What about the CCTVs around the area?</font>

46
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:31,350
<font color="yellow">Don't worry about it, Vice Chairman.</font>

47
00:02:31,780 --> 00:02:33,280
<font color="yellow">Before we stabbed you,</font>

48
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:37,470
<font color="yellow">our boys sprayed all over the CCTVs around the area.</font>

49
00:02:37,470 --> 00:02:39,780
<font color="yellow">Make sure you destroy the car you used.</font>

50
00:02:39,780 --> 00:02:40,850
<font color="yellow">My goodness.</font>

51
00:02:40,850 --> 00:02:45,180
<font color="yellow">It's already been scraped and torn down piece by piece.</font>

52
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:47,470
<font color="yellow">May we report this to the police now?</font>

53
00:02:47,470 --> 00:02:49,190
<font color="yellow">Of course, you may.</font>

54
00:02:49,190 --> 00:02:51,010
<font color="yellow">There is no evidence...</font>

55
00:02:51,010 --> 00:02:53,980
<font color="yellow">and people involved have already went overseas.</font>

56
00:02:59,950 --> 00:03:01,310
<font color="yellow">Are you feeling okay?</font>

57
00:03:02,410 --> 00:03:04,030
<font color="yellow">Yes, I'm okay.</font>

58
00:03:04,030 --> 00:03:05,950
<font color="yellow">I didn't know he'd go this far.</font>

59
00:03:06,410 --> 00:03:08,410
<font color="yellow">There are things you can reach out to take...</font>

60
00:03:08,850 --> 00:03:11,450
<font color="yellow">and things you need to risk your life to get.</font>

61
00:03:11,450 --> 00:03:13,680
<font color="yellow">I don't understand why you had to risk...</font>

62
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:16,210
<font color="yellow">Report my attack to the police...</font>

63
00:03:16,210 --> 00:03:17,730
<font color="yellow">and let the reporters know, too.</font>

64
00:03:17,730 --> 00:03:22,180
<font color="yellow">You should say there was a fight in Dodo Group to become the successor.</font>

65
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:26,070
<font color="yellow">Weren't you going to put this on Il Jae?</font>

66
00:03:26,070 --> 00:03:29,180
<font color="yellow">There is nothing like Il Jae to destroy Gi Tan.</font>

67
00:03:30,010 --> 00:03:31,450
<font color="yellow">I have to protect him a little.</font>

68
00:03:34,150 --> 00:03:35,910
<font color="yellow">It's been reported that Vice Chairman Do Gun Woo...</font>

69
00:03:35,910 --> 00:03:39,250
<font color="yellow">of Dodo Group was attacked by unidentified attackers.</font>

70
00:03:39,250 --> 00:03:42,580
<font color="yellow">He's currently receiving treatment in a hospital downtown,</font>

71
00:03:42,580 --> 00:03:45,910
<font color="yellow">and thankfully, his life is not in danger.</font>

72
00:03:47,210 --> 00:03:50,090
<font color="yellow">Vice Chairman Do Gun Woo has been recognised...</font>

73
00:03:50,090 --> 00:03:52,680
<font color="yellow">for his management skills, and he became the successor...</font>

74
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:55,050
<font color="yellow">of Dodo Group in place of ex-CEO Do Gwang Woo.</font>

75
00:03:55,410 --> 00:03:57,250
<font color="yellow">What kind of news is that?</font>

76
00:03:57,580 --> 00:03:59,450
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo never became the successor.</font>

77
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,510
<font color="yellow">He's very persistent.</font>

78
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:05,880
<font color="yellow">I should've just killed him.</font>

79
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:07,860
<font color="yellow">The police are...</font>

80
00:04:07,860 --> 00:04:09,580
<font color="yellow">focused on this fight between...</font>

81
00:04:09,580 --> 00:04:12,360
<font color="yellow">the two princes to become the successor of Dodo Group...</font>

82
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:16,510
<font color="yellow">and are searching for signs of personal grudges in this incident.</font>

83
00:04:18,380 --> 00:04:20,250
<font color="yellow">I think Gun Woo set this up himself.</font>

84
00:04:20,580 --> 00:04:22,750
<font color="yellow">He's letting people know that he's the successor.</font>

85
00:04:22,750 --> 00:04:24,580
<font color="yellow">He's completely fooled Soo Yeon, too.</font>

86
00:04:26,980 --> 00:04:28,650
<font color="yellow">She needs to know who he really is...</font>

87
00:04:29,210 --> 00:04:30,750
<font color="yellow">before it's too late.</font>

88
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:32,660
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

89
00:04:32,660 --> 00:04:35,380
<font color="yellow">You should just give him pressure with business...</font>

90
00:04:35,380 --> 00:04:37,650
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo is dirty and evil to the point that he'll take...</font>

91
00:04:38,110 --> 00:04:40,080
<font color="yellow">a knife to his stomach.</font>

92
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:42,750
<font color="yellow">He'll side with Il Jae...</font>

93
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:44,650
<font color="yellow">to do away with me.</font>

94
00:04:45,910 --> 00:04:48,210
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon is the only one who'll suffer in the midst of this.</font>

95
00:04:49,320 --> 00:04:50,350
<font color="yellow">You're right.</font>

96
00:04:53,780 --> 00:04:54,820
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

97
00:04:55,580 --> 00:04:57,110
<font color="yellow">You must head to the airport.</font>

98
00:04:58,550 --> 00:05:00,750
<font color="yellow">Did you give Chae Ryung a call?</font>

99
00:05:00,750 --> 00:05:02,350
<font color="yellow">She'll be waiting for you in China.</font>

100
00:05:02,910 --> 00:05:03,950
<font color="yellow">Let's go, Sir.</font>

101
00:05:14,010 --> 00:05:16,710
<font color="yellow">- Gun Woo.
-  Yes. Welcome, Soo Yeon.</font>

102
00:05:17,150 --> 00:05:19,650
<font color="yellow">This is the prosecutor who's in charge of this retrial.</font>

103
00:05:20,150 --> 00:05:21,180
<font color="yellow">My name is Choi Jeong Gook.</font>

104
00:05:21,980 --> 00:05:23,080
<font color="yellow">Nice to meet you.</font>

105
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:36,680
<font color="yellow">Hello?</font>

106
00:05:37,650 --> 00:05:38,750
<font color="yellow">It's me, Gun Woo.</font>

107
00:05:40,780 --> 00:05:42,050
<font color="yellow">Can we talk?</font>

108
00:05:44,310 --> 00:05:45,310
<font color="yellow">Hello?</font>

109
00:05:46,110 --> 00:05:48,550
<font color="yellow">Are you listening to me?</font>

110
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:52,550
<font color="yellow">So you're the prosecutor for Il Jae's retrial, right?</font>

111
00:05:58,650 --> 00:05:59,850
<font color="yellow">I have a guest over.</font>

112
00:05:59,850 --> 00:06:00,980
<font color="yellow">I'll talk to you later.</font>

113
00:06:06,780 --> 00:06:10,180
<font color="yellow">I heard you lost evidence of Il Jae's corruption in this attack.</font>

114
00:06:10,180 --> 00:06:13,610
<font color="yellow">Yes, I was about to hand it over to Lawyer Oh.</font>

115
00:06:14,310 --> 00:06:16,280
<font color="yellow">You didn't mention this to the police.</font>

116
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,750
<font color="yellow">They probably destroyed the evidence already.</font>

117
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:21,840
<font color="yellow">If I mentioned it, I could be filed for making false accusations.</font>

118
00:06:21,840 --> 00:06:24,850
<font color="yellow">Do you also believe that this is his doing?</font>

119
00:06:24,850 --> 00:06:27,770
<font color="yellow">They took the evidence. Isn't it obvious?</font>

120
00:06:27,770 --> 00:06:30,050
<font color="yellow">The media has been saying that it's a fight between successors.</font>

121
00:06:30,050 --> 00:06:33,080
<font color="yellow">Yes, I did that on purpose.</font>

122
00:06:34,380 --> 00:06:37,120
<font color="yellow">I needed to catch Il Jae off-guard...</font>

123
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,740
<font color="yellow">before the retrial.</font>

124
00:06:38,740 --> 00:06:41,920
<font color="yellow">Do you not have a copy of the evidence?</font>

125
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:44,210
<font color="yellow">Yes. Had I known this would've happened,</font>

126
00:06:44,750 --> 00:06:46,480
<font color="yellow">I would've made a copy.</font>

127
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:52,040
<font color="yellow">Will it be difficult for Il Jae to receive additional sentence...</font>

128
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:53,810
<font color="yellow">during this retrial?</font>

129
00:06:54,150 --> 00:06:55,780
<font color="yellow">We'll try even if it doesn't happen.</font>

130
00:06:57,580 --> 00:07:00,010
<font color="yellow">I have to return to the office.</font>

131
00:07:00,780 --> 00:07:02,010
<font color="yellow">I'll be back soon.</font>

132
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:18,450
<font color="yellow">Did you hear that?</font>

133
00:07:19,950 --> 00:07:21,150
<font color="yellow">I had my doubts.</font>

134
00:07:21,910 --> 00:07:24,980
<font color="yellow">Did you stage this yourself? You're amazing, Gun Woo.</font>

135
00:07:25,310 --> 00:07:26,810
<font color="yellow">You catch onto things quickly.</font>

136
00:07:27,850 --> 00:07:31,380
<font color="yellow">Gwang Woo wouldn't stage an attack...</font>

137
00:07:31,910 --> 00:07:33,510
<font color="yellow">to get that evidence.</font>

138
00:07:36,410 --> 00:07:38,560
<font color="yellow">What happened to the evidence?</font>

139
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:40,480
<font color="yellow">I destroyed it. It went up in flames.</font>

140
00:07:41,910 --> 00:07:43,050
<font color="yellow">Destroyed?</font>

141
00:07:43,050 --> 00:07:44,940
<font color="yellow">Yes, as you've heard,</font>

142
00:07:44,940 --> 00:07:48,050
<font color="yellow">your other crimes won't be proved during the retrial.</font>

143
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,680
<font color="yellow">Do you want me...</font>

144
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:53,870
<font color="yellow">to get rid of Gi Tan?</font>

145
00:07:53,870 --> 00:07:56,880
<font color="yellow">Yes. Life is about giving and taking.</font>

146
00:07:58,280 --> 00:07:59,380
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan is the one...</font>

147
00:08:00,210 --> 00:08:04,080
<font color="yellow">who told me that this attack was staged by you.</font>

148
00:08:05,550 --> 00:08:08,050
<font color="yellow">He already knew.</font>

149
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:10,380
<font color="yellow">You should get ready.</font>

150
00:08:13,010 --> 00:08:15,050
<font color="yellow">I don't care. There is no evidence left.</font>

151
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:21,370
<font color="yellow">Come and visit me before the retrial.</font>

152
00:08:21,370 --> 00:08:22,710
<font color="yellow">I have to talk to you.</font>

153
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,680
<font color="yellow">I'm hanging up.</font>

154
00:08:27,580 --> 00:08:29,180
<font color="yellow">Who was that?</font>

155
00:08:29,550 --> 00:08:30,550
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

156
00:08:31,380 --> 00:08:32,850
<font color="yellow">Nothing important.</font>

157
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:35,060
<font color="yellow">You were talking about evidence.</font>

158
00:08:35,060 --> 00:08:38,010
<font color="yellow">It's a reporter. Don't mind it.</font>

159
00:08:38,680 --> 00:08:40,450
<font color="yellow">It's too stuffy in here. Let's go for a walk.</font>

160
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:45,950
<font color="yellow">Once I get out,</font>

161
00:08:46,420 --> 00:08:48,550
<font color="yellow">I'll take care of Gi Tan.</font>

162
00:08:49,150 --> 00:08:52,110
<font color="yellow">I will not let him interfere with your presidential election.</font>

163
00:08:52,110 --> 00:08:53,580
<font color="yellow">Don't worry, Mr Hwang.</font>

164
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:55,550
<font color="yellow">What do you mean...</font>

165
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,280
<font color="yellow">you'll take care of him?</font>

166
00:09:00,210 --> 00:09:01,650
<font color="yellow">I'm going to destroy him.</font>

167
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:04,360
<font color="yellow">If that doesn't go well,</font>

168
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:06,380
<font color="yellow">I will get rid of...</font>

169
00:09:06,380 --> 00:09:07,420
<font color="yellow">Darn you!</font>

170
00:09:08,110 --> 00:09:09,480
<font color="yellow">You're pathetic.</font>

171
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:13,210
<font color="yellow">What if you're found out?</font>

172
00:09:14,550 --> 00:09:17,980
<font color="yellow">It'll be more than just ruining my presidential campaign.</font>

173
00:09:18,710 --> 00:09:21,150
<font color="yellow">You'd be putting a knife on my throat.</font>

174
00:09:23,580 --> 00:09:27,350
<font color="yellow">What do you want me to do then?</font>

175
00:09:35,380 --> 00:09:36,450
<font color="yellow">Here.</font>

176
00:09:41,650 --> 00:09:42,710
<font color="yellow">(Divorce Notice)</font>

177
00:09:46,350 --> 00:09:47,380
<font color="yellow">This is...</font>

178
00:09:49,250 --> 00:09:50,480
<font color="yellow">your stamp.</font>

179
00:09:52,450 --> 00:09:53,750
<font color="yellow">Stamp...</font>

180
00:09:54,350 --> 00:09:55,380
<font color="yellow">the divorce papers.</font>

181
00:09:55,810 --> 00:09:58,180
<font color="yellow">- Sir...
-  If you disappear,</font>

182
00:09:59,420 --> 00:10:04,180
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan won't try to ruin my campaign.</font>

183
00:10:04,180 --> 00:10:06,420
<font color="yellow">Are you cutting your ties with me...</font>

184
00:10:06,420 --> 00:10:08,610
<font color="yellow">because you're scared of Gi Tan?</font>

185
00:10:08,610 --> 00:10:09,750
<font color="yellow">Il Jae!</font>

186
00:10:13,420 --> 00:10:15,310
<font color="yellow">Even if I'm a dragon...</font>

187
00:10:16,210 --> 00:10:18,550
<font color="yellow">flying up into the skies,</font>

188
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:22,980
<font color="yellow">I should be careful no stray dogs are barking at me.</font>

189
00:10:23,580 --> 00:10:25,210
<font color="yellow">It's not because I'm scared.</font>

190
00:10:25,610 --> 00:10:28,380
<font color="yellow">I'm just saying that the presidential campaign...</font>

191
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:32,710
<font color="yellow">must be treated seriously with extra caution.</font>

192
00:10:34,750 --> 00:10:38,880
<font color="yellow">It's not just dogs that could ruin a dragon's path.</font>

193
00:10:42,010 --> 00:10:46,080
<font color="yellow">I didn't want to say this to you but...</font>

194
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,080
<font color="yellow">The prosecutor...</font>

195
00:10:47,920 --> 00:10:52,450
<font color="yellow">assigned to your appeal was chosen by me.</font>

196
00:10:54,710 --> 00:10:55,810
<font color="yellow">Unless you want...</font>

197
00:10:56,980 --> 00:10:59,110
<font color="yellow">to rot in prison forever,</font>

198
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:07,480
<font color="yellow">forget about trying to threaten me...</font>

199
00:11:08,010 --> 00:11:11,580
<font color="yellow">with the fact that Ji Soo is a murderer.</font>

200
00:11:15,150 --> 00:11:17,350
<font color="yellow">I'm not telling you two to separate forever.</font>

201
00:11:18,810 --> 00:11:22,610
<font color="yellow">Once I'm in power,</font>

202
00:11:23,810 --> 00:11:26,880
<font color="yellow">you two can get back together at that point.</font>

203
00:11:27,450 --> 00:11:28,650
<font color="yellow">I can promise you.</font>

204
00:11:30,410 --> 00:11:31,450
<font color="yellow">Did Ji Soo...</font>

205
00:11:32,710 --> 00:11:35,710
<font color="yellow">agree to the divorce?</font>

206
00:11:36,180 --> 00:11:39,110
<font color="yellow">If you stamp on the papers first,</font>

207
00:11:40,780 --> 00:11:42,780
<font color="yellow">I'm sure she'll accept it.</font>

208
00:12:21,010 --> 00:12:22,450
<font color="yellow">You look upset.</font>

209
00:12:22,910 --> 00:12:23,980
<font color="yellow">I just...</font>

210
00:12:24,610 --> 00:12:26,810
<font color="yellow">stamped my divorce papers.</font>

211
00:12:26,810 --> 00:12:27,980
<font color="yellow">What do you mean, a divorce?</font>

212
00:12:28,650 --> 00:12:31,250
<font color="yellow">Are you getting a divorce with Congresswoman Hwang?</font>

