<font color="yellow">What does he have?</font>

635
00:39:13,680 --> 00:39:16,350
<font color="yellow">The side effects of his medication...</font>

636
00:39:16,680 --> 00:39:19,410
<font color="yellow">Are you saying his medication caused dementia?</font>

637
00:39:19,850 --> 00:39:21,180
<font color="yellow">It's not dementia.</font>

638
00:39:21,180 --> 00:39:22,380
<font color="yellow">Dr Hwang!</font>

639
00:39:23,310 --> 00:39:25,180
<font color="yellow">You appeared on TV...</font>

640
00:39:25,710 --> 00:39:28,980
<font color="yellow">and we gave you a plaque for your outstanding services.</font>

641
00:39:30,110 --> 00:39:31,150
<font color="yellow">Must I...</font>

642
00:39:31,650 --> 00:39:34,650
<font color="yellow">reveal your true colours to make you tell the truth?</font>

643
00:39:37,110 --> 00:39:38,310
<font color="yellow">Do Choong.</font>

644
00:39:40,380 --> 00:39:41,880
<font color="yellow">What illness does he have?</font>

645
00:39:45,180 --> 00:39:46,180
<font color="yellow">It is...</font>

646
00:39:47,650 --> 00:39:48,680
<font color="yellow">dementia.</font>

647
00:39:52,910 --> 00:39:53,910
<font color="yellow">It is...</font>

648
00:39:54,410 --> 00:39:56,150
<font color="yellow">getting worse.</font>

649
00:39:56,150 --> 00:39:57,280
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo.</font>

650
00:39:58,650 --> 00:40:00,550
<font color="yellow">Did he pay you off...</font>

651
00:40:01,850 --> 00:40:03,350
<font color="yellow">to keep quiet?</font>

652
00:40:03,710 --> 00:40:04,710
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

653
00:40:05,410 --> 00:40:06,410
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

654
00:40:08,310 --> 00:40:09,410
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

655
00:40:14,520 --> 00:40:16,890
<font color="yellow">Does he really have dementia?</font>

656
00:40:16,890 --> 00:40:19,080
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo told Doctor Hwang...</font>

657
00:40:19,410 --> 00:40:21,680
<font color="yellow">to keep it a secret until...</font>

658
00:40:21,680 --> 00:40:24,000
<font color="yellow">the inheritance has been distributed.</font>

659
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:26,950
<font color="yellow">That means he's hiding Father's illness...</font>

660
00:40:27,310 --> 00:40:29,710
<font color="yellow">so he can take what isn't his.</font>

661
00:40:30,020 --> 00:40:32,020
<font color="yellow">It's pretty obvious what he's up to.</font>

662
00:40:32,520 --> 00:40:33,520
<font color="yellow">He's so evil.</font>

663
00:40:33,950 --> 00:40:36,290
<font color="yellow">How could he do such a thing?</font>

664
00:40:36,290 --> 00:40:38,640
<font color="yellow">You're just as bad.</font>

665
00:40:38,640 --> 00:40:40,450
<font color="yellow">You swapped his medication.</font>

666
00:40:40,450 --> 00:40:41,590
<font color="yellow">Are you...</font>

667
00:40:41,590 --> 00:40:43,250
<font color="yellow">fanning the flames?</font>

668
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:51,680
<font color="yellow">Who are you calling?</font>

669
00:40:52,110 --> 00:40:53,610
<font color="yellow">We can't waste time.</font>

670
00:40:54,150 --> 00:40:56,080
<font color="yellow">We have to tell Father...</font>

671
00:40:56,080 --> 00:40:57,910
<font color="yellow">what Gun Woo is really up to.</font>

672
00:40:59,280 --> 00:41:00,810
<font color="yellow">Goodness.</font>

673
00:41:01,380 --> 00:41:03,650
<font color="yellow">- Hello?
-  It's me, Gwang Woo.</font>

674
00:41:04,480 --> 00:41:05,610
<font color="yellow">Hang up.</font>

675
00:41:06,180 --> 00:41:08,450
<font color="yellow">You're being deceived.</font>

676
00:41:08,450 --> 00:41:09,750
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

677
00:41:10,310 --> 00:41:11,310
<font color="yellow">You...</font>

678
00:41:11,780 --> 00:41:13,350
<font color="yellow">have dementia.</font>

679
00:41:13,780 --> 00:41:15,610
<font color="yellow">What? Dementia?</font>

680
00:41:17,050 --> 00:41:19,150
<font color="yellow">Yes, dementia.</font>

681
00:41:19,750 --> 00:41:21,350
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo and Doctor Hwang...</font>

682
00:41:22,050 --> 00:41:24,980
<font color="yellow">ganged up on you to hoodwink you.</font>

683
00:41:29,880 --> 00:41:31,780
<font color="yellow">Are you listening?</font>

684
00:41:32,180 --> 00:41:33,310
<font color="yellow">Keep talking.</font>

685
00:41:35,410 --> 00:41:38,350
<font color="yellow">You're rewriting your will, aren't you?</font>

686
00:41:39,150 --> 00:41:40,550
<font color="yellow">Stop it right now.</font>

687
00:41:41,180 --> 00:41:43,470
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo's putting you in danger...</font>

688
00:41:43,470 --> 00:41:45,910
<font color="yellow">so he can take everything you have.</font>

689
00:41:47,110 --> 00:41:49,290
<font color="yellow">Where are you right now?</font>

690
00:41:49,290 --> 00:41:50,480
<font color="yellow">I'll come over...</font>

691
00:41:50,880 --> 00:41:52,180
<font color="yellow">and explain everything.</font>

692
00:41:53,020 --> 00:41:54,020
<font color="yellow">Gwang Woo.</font>

693
00:41:55,910 --> 00:41:57,050
<font color="yellow">Yes, Father.</font>

694
00:41:57,380 --> 00:41:58,680
<font color="yellow">Dementia?</font>

695
00:41:59,410 --> 00:42:01,410
<font color="yellow">Why don't you pray that I die?</font>

696
00:42:01,850 --> 00:42:03,680
<font color="yellow">How dare you talk such nonsense!</font>

697
00:42:04,580 --> 00:42:05,730
<font color="yellow">Father.</font>

698
00:42:05,730 --> 00:42:09,660
<font color="yellow">I filed for a restraining order against you.</font>

699
00:42:09,660 --> 00:42:11,580
<font color="yellow">Come by and see what happens.</font>

700
00:42:13,180 --> 00:42:16,580
<font color="yellow">A restraining order?</font>

701
00:42:17,410 --> 00:42:18,650
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

702
00:42:19,310 --> 00:42:21,880
<font color="yellow">A restraining order?</font>

703
00:42:21,880 --> 00:42:23,910
<font color="yellow">For as long as I live,</font>

704
00:42:23,910 --> 00:42:26,080
<font color="yellow">I will fight to take back the assets I gave...</font>

705
00:42:26,910 --> 00:42:28,860
<font color="yellow">to you and your mother.</font>

706
00:42:28,860 --> 00:42:31,380
<font color="yellow">Let's see you two end up without a penny!</font>

707
00:42:42,410 --> 00:42:44,750
<font color="yellow">Did he just say...</font>

708
00:42:45,280 --> 00:42:47,550
<font color="yellow">he filed for a restraining order?</font>

709
00:42:47,950 --> 00:42:48,950
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

710
00:42:50,080 --> 00:42:52,580
<font color="yellow">This is all Gun Woo's fault.</font>

711
00:42:54,150 --> 00:42:55,150
<font color="yellow">He is...</font>

712
00:42:55,950 --> 00:42:58,380
<font color="yellow">controlling Father like a puppet.</font>

713
00:43:01,850 --> 00:43:03,710
<font color="yellow">What should we do?</font>

714
00:43:05,380 --> 00:43:06,680
<font color="yellow">Help us, Jae Man.</font>

715
00:43:20,880 --> 00:43:22,480
<font color="yellow">How dare he make me...</font>

716
00:43:23,520 --> 00:43:24,610
<font color="yellow">as a dementia patient?</font>

717
00:43:26,680 --> 00:43:28,780
<font color="yellow">If I don't keep my wits about me,</font>

718
00:43:29,180 --> 00:43:32,110
<font color="yellow">they might take things from under my nose.</font>

719
00:43:35,810 --> 00:43:36,850
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

720
00:43:37,380 --> 00:43:39,310
<font color="yellow">I'd like to have dinner with you.</font>

721
00:43:39,850 --> 00:43:42,180
<font color="yellow">I'm in no mood for that. Let's eat...</font>

722
00:43:42,180 --> 00:43:43,310
<font color="yellow">This is Kang Gi Tan.</font>

723
00:43:50,480 --> 00:43:53,450
<font color="yellow">Are you busy preparing for the appeal?</font>

724
00:43:53,880 --> 00:43:57,010
<font color="yellow">We have to make sure Il Jae remains behind bars.</font>

725
00:44:00,110 --> 00:44:02,650
<font color="yellow">What's a vice chairman doing skipping meals?</font>

726
00:44:03,380 --> 00:44:04,910
<font color="yellow">I had a long day.</font>

727
00:44:05,310 --> 00:44:07,150
<font color="yellow">Can you not get a loan?</font>

728
00:44:10,880 --> 00:44:11,880
<font color="yellow">I can't.</font>

729
00:44:12,310 --> 00:44:16,580
<font color="yellow">I think Gi Tan got to the banks before I did.</font>

730
00:44:16,910 --> 00:44:18,250
<font color="yellow">Why would he?</font>

731
00:44:18,250 --> 00:44:20,910
<font color="yellow">I think he wants Dodo Group.</font>

732
00:44:21,280 --> 00:44:23,480
<font color="yellow">That might be why he keeps Shin Young close.</font>

733
00:44:24,110 --> 00:44:26,650
<font color="yellow">He approached her on purpose?</font>

734
00:44:27,310 --> 00:44:28,710
<font color="yellow">I'm sure I'm right.</font>

735
00:44:30,650 --> 00:44:32,680
<font color="yellow">He wouldn't do such a thing.</font>

736
00:44:36,180 --> 00:44:37,450
<font color="yellow">Have you...</font>

737
00:44:37,450 --> 00:44:39,110
<font color="yellow">heard from him?</font>

738
00:44:39,880 --> 00:44:41,350
<font color="yellow">No. I guess he's busy.</font>

739
00:44:41,910 --> 00:44:44,480
<font color="yellow">I was too busy with the trial to call him too.</font>

740
00:44:46,110 --> 00:44:47,180
<font color="yellow">His memory...</font>

741
00:44:47,850 --> 00:44:49,610
<font color="yellow">must be back by now.</font>

742
00:44:51,380 --> 00:44:52,750
<font color="yellow">What are you thinking about?</font>

743
00:44:53,710 --> 00:44:54,750
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

744
00:44:55,310 --> 00:44:56,350
<font color="yellow">Nothing.</font>

745
00:44:59,250 --> 00:45:00,710
<font color="yellow">(Kang Gi Tan)</font>

746
00:45:04,010 --> 00:45:05,010
<font color="yellow">What do you want?</font>

747
00:45:05,850 --> 00:45:07,150
<font color="yellow">I have something to say.</font>

748
00:45:07,480 --> 00:45:08,510
<font color="yellow">Shall we meet?</font>

749
00:45:09,680 --> 00:45:12,250
<font color="yellow">I'm on my way to a dinner appointment.</font>

750
00:45:13,310 --> 00:45:14,510
<font color="yellow">Do you want to join us?</font>

751
00:45:14,880 --> 00:45:16,100
<font color="yellow">Can I?</font>

752
00:45:16,100 --> 00:45:17,110
<font color="yellow">Of course.</font>

753
00:45:17,910 --> 00:45:19,550
<font color="yellow">You know everyone.</font>

754
00:45:20,580 --> 00:45:21,610
<font color="yellow">Give me the address.</font>

755
00:45:22,110 --> 00:45:23,110
<font color="yellow">Write it down, Soo Yeon.</font>

756
00:45:23,510 --> 00:45:24,510
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

757
00:45:26,610 --> 00:45:27,610
<font color="yellow">Are you...</font>

758
00:45:28,710 --> 00:45:30,510
<font color="yellow">with Soo Yeon right now?</font>

759
00:45:32,380 --> 00:45:35,580
<font color="yellow">Yes. I'm at her place eating dinner.</font>

760
00:45:38,880 --> 00:45:40,120
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

761
00:45:40,120 --> 00:45:41,380
<font color="yellow">Can't you breathe?</font>

762
00:45:43,110 --> 00:45:44,110
<font color="yellow">I'm fine.</font>

763
00:45:45,910 --> 00:45:47,090
<font color="yellow">You...</font>

764
00:45:47,090 --> 00:45:48,780
<font color="yellow">must be with Shin Young.</font>

765
00:45:50,310 --> 00:45:51,980
<font color="yellow">I'll text you the address.</font>

766
00:45:54,050 --> 00:45:55,350
<font color="yellow">Be there.</font>

767
00:46:03,880 --> 00:46:05,580
<font color="yellow">Am I allowed to be there?</font>

768
00:46:06,410 --> 00:46:08,750
<font color="yellow">I'm going to ask Gi Tan for funds.</font>

769
00:46:09,410 --> 00:46:11,510
<font color="yellow">You can offer some moral support.</font>

770
00:46:23,010 --> 00:46:25,110
<font color="yellow">Welcome, Gun Woo.</font>

771
00:46:25,510 --> 00:46:26,680
<font color="yellow">Hello, Lawyer Oh.</font>

772
00:46:28,510 --> 00:46:29,610
<font color="yellow">Have a seat.</font>

773
00:46:38,410 --> 00:46:40,260
<font color="yellow">Why are you here, Father?</font>

774
00:46:40,260 --> 00:46:41,310
<font color="yellow">Say hello.</font>

775
00:46:41,910 --> 00:46:45,080
<font color="yellow">He's the vice chairman of Gold Bank in Hong Kong.</font>

776
00:46:45,080 --> 00:46:47,250
<font color="yellow">Nice to meet you. I'm Johnny Kim.</font>

777
00:46:47,580 --> 00:46:49,120
<font color="yellow">I'm Do Gun Woo.</font>

778
00:46:49,120 --> 00:46:50,710
<font color="yellow">Gold Bank offered...</font>

779
00:46:51,310 --> 00:46:53,150
<font color="yellow">to lend you the money...</font>

780
00:46:53,610 --> 00:46:56,150
<font color="yellow">with a refund guarantee.</font>

781
00:46:57,810 --> 00:47:00,250
<font color="yellow">Chairman K negotiated the deal.</font>

782
00:47:05,180 --> 00:47:07,280
<font color="yellow">I should go, Sir.</font>

783
00:47:07,880 --> 00:47:09,180
<font color="yellow">I will walk you out.</font>

784
00:47:10,280 --> 00:47:11,410
<font color="yellow">I won't go far.</font>

785
00:47:14,810 --> 00:47:16,150
<font color="yellow">You helped us...</font>

786
00:47:16,650 --> 00:47:19,450
<font color="yellow">avert a huge crisis.</font>

787
00:47:20,110 --> 00:47:21,450
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

788
00:47:21,450 --> 00:47:24,110
<font color="yellow">I saw you run left and right trying to secure funding.</font>

789
00:47:24,880 --> 00:47:26,900
<font color="yellow">It upset Shin Young, too.</font>

790
00:47:26,900 --> 00:47:28,870
<font color="yellow">She asked me to intervene.</font>

791
00:47:28,870 --> 00:47:30,310
<font color="yellow">Chairman K...</font>

792
00:47:30,310 --> 00:47:33,510
<font color="yellow">does anything and everything I ask him to.</font>

793
00:47:36,180 --> 00:47:37,450
<font color="yellow">What do you think?</font>

794
00:47:37,910 --> 00:47:41,410
<font color="yellow">Don't you think they make a lovely couple?</font>

795
00:47:43,110 --> 00:47:44,380
<font color="yellow">They do.</font>

796
00:47:44,380 --> 00:47:46,910
<font color="yellow">I wholeheartedly support their marriage.</font>

797
00:47:50,180 --> 00:47:53,080
<font color="yellow">What made you side with me this time?</font>

798
00:47:54,410 --> 00:47:57,480
<font color="yellow">There are rumours that Gun Woo will marry Lawyer Oh.</font>

799
00:47:58,510 --> 00:48:00,380
<font color="yellow">Do you have your father's approval?</font>

800
00:48:00,810 --> 00:48:01,910
<font color="yellow">No, no.</font>

801
00:48:02,310 --> 00:48:03,510
<font color="yellow">That's not true.</font>

802
00:48:04,380 --> 00:48:07,180
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo has no intention of getting married yet.</font>

803
00:48:12,880 --> 00:48:14,280
<font color="yellow">You know his condition.</font>

804
00:48:14,880 --> 00:48:15,910
<font color="yellow">Don't get upset.</font>

805
00:48:18,310 --> 00:48:20,250
<font color="yellow">You look sweet together.</font>

806
00:48:20,810 --> 00:48:22,080
<font color="yellow">Dad.</font>

807
00:48:22,080 --> 00:48:25,780
<font color="yellow">Don't you think Gun Woo and Lawyer Oh would get along well?</font>

808
00:48:25,780 --> 00:48:27,180
<font color="yellow">Let's stop talking about that.</font>

809
00:48:27,750 --> 00:48:28,860
<font color="yellow">Lawyer Oh.</font>

810
00:48:28,860 --> 00:48:29,910
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

811
00:48:30,780 --> 00:48:34,850
<font color="yellow">When I amend your will, I'll revise the percentage of inheritance.</font>

812
00:48:37,610 --> 00:48:38,750
<font color="yellow">Shin Young gets 50 percent.</font>

813
00:48:40,710 --> 00:48:41,810
<font color="yellow">So does Gun Woo.</font>

814
00:48:45,010 --> 00:48:46,110
<font color="yellow">Thanks, Dad.</font>

815
00:48:54,810 --> 00:48:58,380
<font color="yellow">Now, I know why you offered to finance...</font>

816
00:48:58,380 --> 00:48:59,510
<font color="yellow">the shipbuilding project.</font>

817
00:49:00,280 --> 00:49:02,880
<font color="yellow">Are you the one who talked to the bank managers?</font>

818
00:49:06,380 --> 00:49:09,010
<font color="yellow">One hand holds a carrot, the other a whip.</font>

819
00:49:10,580 --> 00:49:11,880
<font color="yellow">Thanks for the lesson.</font>

820
00:49:11,880 --> 00:49:14,650
<font color="yellow">I still have a lot to teach you. If you want to learn,</font>

821
00:49:15,280 --> 00:49:17,280
<font color="yellow">- try being humble.
-  Do you...</font>

822
00:49:18,080 --> 00:49:19,710
<font color="yellow">remember your past...</font>

823
00:49:21,110 --> 00:49:22,450
<font color="yellow">with Soo Yeon?</font>

824
00:49:25,610 --> 00:49:28,780
<font color="yellow">Is your memory back?</font>

825
00:49:30,480 --> 00:49:31,550
<font color="yellow">It is.</font>

826
00:49:32,410 --> 00:49:33,850
<font color="yellow">In its full detail.</font>

827
00:49:36,410 --> 00:49:38,250
<font color="yellow">You can take the upper hand in business,</font>

828
00:49:39,780 --> 00:49:42,400
<font color="yellow">but I will not give up Soo Yeon.</font>

829
00:49:42,400 --> 00:49:45,780
<font color="yellow">Don't dream of taking her back. Give up while you can.</font>

830
00:49:46,150 --> 00:49:47,250
<font color="yellow">I already did.</font>

831
00:49:48,110 --> 00:49:49,180
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

832
00:49:49,580 --> 00:49:51,410
<font color="yellow">I don't care about her.</font>

833
00:49:52,980 --> 00:49:55,280
<font color="yellow">You wouldn't say something like that.</font>

834
00:49:55,880 --> 00:49:59,380
<font color="yellow">I guess you spread the rumour that you two were engaged.</font>

835
00:50:00,180 --> 00:50:03,510
<font color="yellow">Don't worry. I will marry her.</font>

836
00:50:04,110 --> 00:50:05,310
<font color="yellow">Focus on the business.</font>

837
00:50:06,380 --> 00:50:07,880
<font color="yellow">Lose Dodo Group...</font>

838
00:50:08,750 --> 00:50:10,250
<font color="yellow">and you lose Soo Yeon, too.</font>

839
00:50:25,910 --> 00:50:27,310
<font color="yellow">What did you say?</font>

840
00:50:27,310 --> 00:50:30,180
<font color="yellow">Stop flirting with my Gi Tan.</font>

841
00:50:30,180 --> 00:50:32,300
<font color="yellow">Do you think I'm flirting with him?</font>

842
00:50:32,300 --> 00:50:34,110
<font color="yellow">Yes, I do.</font>

843
00:50:34,550 --> 00:50:37,250
<font color="yellow">I can see all nine of your foxy tails.</font>

844
00:50:37,250 --> 00:50:38,550
<font color="yellow">They squirm.</font>

845
00:50:39,250 --> 00:50:41,950
<font color="yellow">- Maybe you're just insecure.
-  What?</font>

846
00:50:43,380 --> 00:50:46,540
<font color="yellow">Do you think you're a match for me?</font>

847
00:50:46,540 --> 00:50:48,410
<font color="yellow">If you don't think so,</font>

848
00:50:48,850 --> 00:50:50,070
<font color="yellow">then don't mind me.</font>

849
00:50:50,070 --> 00:50:51,250
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon.</font>

850
00:50:51,250 --> 00:50:53,010
<font color="yellow">Do you know what love is?</font>

851
00:50:53,010 --> 00:50:55,110
<font color="yellow">I do. I know very well.</font>

852
00:50:55,110 --> 00:50:57,110
<font color="yellow">No, you don't know.</font>

853
00:50:57,850 --> 00:50:59,750
<font color="yellow">It hurts you so deep...</font>

854
00:51:03,710 --> 00:51:05,710
<font color="yellow">Are you trying to lecture me?</font>

855
00:51:08,350 --> 00:51:09,980
<font color="yellow">If you want to love Gi Tan,</font>

856
00:51:10,910 --> 00:51:13,080
<font color="yellow">find out where he hurts the most.</font>

857
00:51:13,550 --> 00:51:15,680
<font color="yellow">Stop acting like a selfish child.</font>

858
00:51:17,410 --> 00:51:19,310
<font color="yellow">Being able to suffer with him...</font>

859
00:51:20,780 --> 00:51:22,810
<font color="yellow">gives you the right to love him.</font>

860
00:51:32,510 --> 00:51:33,780
<font color="yellow">What a brat.</font>

861
00:51:39,550 --> 00:51:42,280
<font color="yellow">Why do I feel like I just lost?</font>

862
00:51:49,780 --> 00:51:50,950
<font color="yellow">Are you leaving?</font>

863
00:51:52,080 --> 00:51:53,150
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

864
00:51:53,850 --> 00:51:55,810
<font color="yellow">You didn't eat much earlier.</font>

865
00:51:56,610 --> 00:51:59,550
<font color="yellow">Don't worry about me. I should go.</font>

866
00:51:59,950 --> 00:52:00,950
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon.</font>

867
00:52:04,450 --> 00:52:06,280
<font color="yellow">I'll call you that from now on.</font>

868
00:52:08,250 --> 00:52:11,000
<font color="yellow">Please don't. It makes me feel uncomfortable.</font>

869
00:52:11,000 --> 00:52:13,080
<font color="yellow">We used to be close colleagues.</font>

870
00:52:14,180 --> 00:52:18,110
<font color="yellow">Maybe you thought we were close, but I didn't think so.</font>

871
00:52:21,650 --> 00:52:25,310
<font color="yellow">I apologise. I didn't mean to make you feel uncomfortable.</font>

872
00:52:45,780 --> 00:52:46,780
<font color="yellow">Here you go.</font>

873
00:52:47,280 --> 00:52:48,450
<font color="yellow">- Eat up.
-  Thanks.</font>

874
00:52:53,350 --> 00:52:54,450
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

875
00:52:55,250 --> 00:52:58,850
<font color="yellow">What brings you to our tiny office?</font>

876
00:52:59,510 --> 00:53:01,180
<font color="yellow">- Send everyone out.
-  Pardon?</font>

877
00:53:02,080 --> 00:53:05,180
<font color="yellow">They were just about to eat their noodles.</font>

878
00:53:07,310 --> 00:53:08,380
<font color="yellow">Get out.</font>

879
00:53:09,050 --> 00:53:12,110
<font color="yellow">You can take the noodles with you.</font>

880
00:53:26,580 --> 00:53:27,850
<font color="yellow">What do you want?</font>

881
00:53:27,850 --> 00:53:31,610
<font color="yellow">Drop everything else and keep an eye on Kang Gi Tan.</font>

882
00:53:31,610 --> 00:53:33,250
<font color="yellow">- What?
-  Find out where he goes,</font>

883
00:53:33,250 --> 00:53:35,150
<font color="yellow">what he does and who he meets.</font>

884
00:53:35,150 --> 00:53:37,050
<font color="yellow">I want a full report on everything.</font>

885
00:53:37,550 --> 00:53:40,250
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir. I'll put my boys...</font>

886
00:53:40,250 --> 00:53:42,410
<font color="yellow">- Do it yourself.
-  Me?</font>

887
00:53:44,510 --> 00:53:47,250
<font color="yellow">I'm pretty high up the ladder now. I don't do...</font>

888
00:53:47,250 --> 00:53:48,650
<font color="yellow">Do as you're told.</font>

889
00:53:53,280 --> 00:53:54,350
<font color="yellow">Yang Dong Yi.</font>

890
00:53:54,780 --> 00:53:58,050
<font color="yellow">Don't try to pull anything. I'm not like Gwang Woo.</font>

891
00:54:00,010 --> 00:54:01,680
<font color="yellow">I get what you mean.</font>

892
00:54:02,050 --> 00:54:03,450
<font color="yellow">I'll do it myself.</font>

893
00:54:04,580 --> 00:54:07,600
<font color="yellow">They're quick to notice things. Don't get caught.</font>

894
00:54:07,600 --> 00:54:08,910
<font color="yellow">I won't, Sir.</font>

895
00:54:15,980 --> 00:54:17,110
<font color="yellow">Checkmate.</font>

896
00:54:19,550 --> 00:54:22,180
<font color="yellow">Oh dear, I didn't see the cannon there.</font>

897
00:54:23,580 --> 00:54:25,480
<font color="yellow">Dodo Group's loan from Gold Bank...</font>

898
00:54:25,480 --> 00:54:27,970
<font color="yellow">means we practically control their finances.</font>

899
00:54:27,970 --> 00:54:29,750
<font color="yellow">What should come next?</font>

900
00:54:31,110 --> 00:54:32,350
<font color="yellow">Out of check.</font>

901
00:54:32,850 --> 00:54:34,580
<font color="yellow">Wouldn't it be liabilities?</font>

902
00:54:34,580 --> 00:54:35,650
<font color="yellow">Correct.</font>

903
00:54:36,280 --> 00:54:37,880
<font color="yellow">Once we control their debt,</font>

904
00:54:38,250 --> 00:54:41,760
<font color="yellow">we control most of Dodo Group.</font>

905
00:54:41,760 --> 00:54:44,580
<font color="yellow">The audit files I saw when I worked there...</font>

906
00:54:45,010 --> 00:54:47,810
<font color="yellow">listed a lot of bonds that mature this year.</font>

907
00:54:48,280 --> 00:54:50,110
<font color="yellow">Could you get a list of the owners...</font>

908
00:54:50,810 --> 00:54:52,280
<font color="yellow">of those bonds?</font>

909
00:54:52,750 --> 00:54:56,370
<font color="yellow">That shouldn't be too hard. I still know people who work there.</font>

910
00:54:56,370 --> 00:54:59,580
<font color="yellow">But most of the owners of the bonds...</font>

911
00:54:59,910 --> 00:55:01,380
<font color="yellow">are loan sharks.</font>

912
00:55:01,380 --> 00:55:02,910
<font color="yellow">Loan sharks?</font>

913
00:55:04,950 --> 00:55:06,050
<font color="yellow">Checkmate.</font>

914
00:55:07,580 --> 00:55:09,750
<font color="yellow">You got me again.</font>

915
00:55:10,710 --> 00:55:12,510
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo is on high alert.</font>

916
00:55:12,850 --> 00:55:14,580
<font color="yellow">We have to buy the bonds...</font>

917
00:55:15,180 --> 00:55:18,250
<font color="yellow">before he notices.</font>

918
00:55:24,380 --> 00:55:25,480
<font color="yellow">Loan sharks?</font>

919
00:55:26,080 --> 00:55:28,850
<font color="yellow">He's sniffing around private money markets?</font>

920
00:55:28,850 --> 00:55:31,680
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan doesn't move in person.</font>

921
00:55:32,350 --> 00:55:35,250
<font color="yellow">Moon Tae Gwang's doing all the legwork.</font>

922
00:55:37,510 --> 00:55:40,480
<font color="yellow">It didn't look like he was borrowing money.</font>

923
00:55:42,050 --> 00:55:43,180
<font color="yellow">Bonds.</font>

924
00:55:43,710 --> 00:55:44,810
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

925
00:55:45,350 --> 00:55:46,750
<font color="yellow">The matured bonds.</font>

926
00:55:46,750 --> 00:55:49,250
<font color="yellow">That's what he's after.</font>

927
00:55:50,150 --> 00:55:53,950
<font color="yellow">I heard that someone there owns a lot of bonds...</font>

928
00:55:53,950 --> 00:55:55,410
<font color="yellow">belonging to Dodo Group.</font>

929
00:55:56,080 --> 00:55:59,110
<font color="yellow">We have to stop him. If Gi Tan buys those bonds,</font>

930
00:55:59,510 --> 00:56:00,850
<font color="yellow">then Dodo Group is doomed.</font>

931
00:56:02,050 --> 00:56:03,950
<font color="yellow">The day we get the matured bonds...</font>

932
00:56:04,550 --> 00:56:06,550
<font color="yellow">will be the day Dodo Group shuts down.</font>

933
00:56:07,010 --> 00:56:10,010
<font color="yellow">Don't you think you should meet one of the bigger financiers?</font>

934
00:56:10,410 --> 00:56:12,810
<font color="yellow">- I should.
-  I heard that...</font>

935
00:56:12,810 --> 00:56:14,580
<font color="yellow">he's pretty cranky.</font>

936
00:56:14,580 --> 00:56:16,710
<font color="yellow">Don't worry. I can deal with that.</font>

937
00:56:17,880 --> 00:56:21,280
<font color="yellow">Il Jae's appeal begins today. Shouldn't you be there?</font>

938
00:56:22,150 --> 00:56:23,250
<font color="yellow">I should.</font>

939
00:56:24,180 --> 00:56:27,950
<font color="yellow">I'd love to see him scrunch up his ugly face.</font>

940
00:56:33,750 --> 00:56:35,180
<font color="yellow">- How does that feel?
-  Good.</font>

941
00:56:47,250 --> 00:56:49,350
<font color="yellow">I wish you luck today.</font>

942
00:56:49,850 --> 00:56:53,450
<font color="yellow">I won't be coming back here.</font>

943
00:56:54,710 --> 00:56:55,850
<font color="yellow">I'll pray for you.</font>

944
00:56:59,580 --> 00:57:00,750
<font color="yellow">Choong Dong.</font>

945
00:57:01,480 --> 00:57:04,820
<font color="yellow">You might have to stay here a little longer.</font>

946
00:57:04,820 --> 00:57:06,080
<font color="yellow">Don't worry about me.</font>

947
00:57:07,150 --> 00:57:10,810
<font color="yellow">I'll do what I can to get you paroled soon.</font>

948
00:57:31,310 --> 00:57:34,350
<font color="yellow">Is Prosecutor Choi worth trusting?</font>

949
00:57:36,180 --> 00:57:38,850
<font color="yellow">He said he'd go for the highest sentence possible.</font>

950
00:58:05,780 --> 00:58:08,350
<font color="yellow">All rise and greet the judge.</font>

951
00:58:14,180 --> 00:58:17,080
<font color="yellow">Are you sure you want to announce your candidacy today?</font>

952
00:58:17,580 --> 00:58:18,750
<font color="yellow">Ji Soo.</font>

953
00:58:19,250 --> 00:58:20,850
<font color="yellow">I survived...</font>

954
00:58:21,980 --> 00:58:24,080
<font color="yellow">the corrupt world of politics...</font>

955
00:58:24,610 --> 00:58:26,720
<font color="yellow">for this day.</font>

956
00:58:26,720 --> 00:58:28,450
<font color="yellow">That's what worries me.</font>

957
00:58:29,310 --> 00:58:32,580
<font color="yellow">Il Jae's trial begins today and I don't want that...</font>

958
00:58:32,580 --> 00:58:34,750
<font color="yellow">to get you into trouble again.</font>

959
00:58:34,750 --> 00:58:36,480
<font color="yellow">Don't worry about that.</font>

960
00:58:37,810 --> 00:58:40,980
<font color="yellow">While I campaign to become president,</font>

961
00:58:40,980 --> 00:58:44,150
<font color="yellow">I will not have to worry about Il Jae.</font>

962
00:58:48,680 --> 00:58:50,910
<font color="yellow">It's time to leave for your press conference.</font>

963
00:58:51,610 --> 00:58:52,650
<font color="yellow">Sure.</font>

964
00:58:53,850 --> 00:58:54,950
<font color="yellow">Bye.</font>

965
00:58:57,610 --> 00:58:58,980
<font color="yellow">Byun Il Jae.</font>

966
00:58:59,510 --> 00:59:02,980
<font color="yellow">You bribed another candidate...</font>

967
00:59:03,510 --> 00:59:07,420
<font color="yellow">and we have clear evidence you tried to cover it up.</font>

968
00:59:07,420 --> 00:59:09,510
<font color="yellow">You violated election laws.</font>

969
00:59:13,550 --> 00:59:14,550
<font color="yellow">However,</font>

970
00:59:15,080 --> 00:59:16,950
<font color="yellow">the charges of abduction and...</font>

971
00:59:17,450 --> 00:59:19,350
<font color="yellow">attempted murder of lawyer Oh Soo Yeon...</font>

972
00:59:19,810 --> 00:59:21,110
<font color="yellow">lacks evidence.</font>

973
00:59:21,550 --> 00:59:23,180
<font color="yellow">I will not charge you for that.</font>

974
00:59:23,750 --> 00:59:26,480
<font color="yellow">Therefore, this court sentences Byun Il Jae...</font>

975
00:59:26,950 --> 00:59:30,250
<font color="yellow">to two years in prison and three years in probation.</font>

976
00:59:33,950 --> 00:59:36,280
<font color="yellow">Doesn't that mean he gets out?</font>

977
00:59:36,680 --> 00:59:38,950
<font color="yellow">What kind of a paralegal doesn't know that?</font>

978
01:00:07,250 --> 01:00:09,280
<font color="yellow">Mr Hwang Jae Man is here.</font>

979
01:00:15,910 --> 01:00:25,050
<font color="yellow">- Hwang Jae Man.
-  Hwang Jae Man.</font>

980
01:00:25,050 --> 01:00:26,410
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

981
01:00:27,150 --> 01:00:28,150
<font color="yellow">Take your seats.</font>

982
01:00:30,150 --> 01:00:32,080
<font color="yellow">Could I ask you a question first?</font>

983
01:00:32,510 --> 01:00:33,850
<font color="yellow">Your son-in-law...</font>

984
01:00:33,850 --> 01:00:36,750
<font color="yellow">mayoral elect Byun Il Jae's appeal is underway right now.</font>

985
01:00:37,180 --> 01:00:39,180
<font color="yellow">Isn't this a bad time to run for president?</font>

986
01:00:39,650 --> 01:00:41,310
<font color="yellow">You're getting ahead of yourself.</font>

987
01:00:43,150 --> 01:00:45,550
<font color="yellow">I see you aren't aware that...</font>

988
01:00:46,610 --> 01:00:47,750
<font color="yellow">Byun Il Jae...</font>

989
01:00:48,250 --> 01:00:49,380
<font color="yellow">is no longer...</font>

990
01:00:49,810 --> 01:00:51,380
<font color="yellow">my son-in-law.</font>

991
01:00:53,850 --> 01:00:55,950
<font color="yellow">He is in the process...</font>

992
01:00:56,710 --> 01:00:58,750
<font color="yellow">of divorcing my daughter.</font>

993
01:00:59,980 --> 01:01:01,280
<font color="yellow">If you don't believe me,</font>

994
01:01:01,850 --> 01:01:03,950
<font color="yellow">once we are done here,</font>

995
01:01:03,950 --> 01:01:06,780
<font color="yellow">check the public records yourselves.</font>

996
01:01:12,950 --> 01:01:13,980
<font color="yellow">Where are you going?</font>

997
01:01:14,910 --> 01:01:17,160
<font color="yellow">The prosecutor broke every promise he made.</font>

998
01:01:17,160 --> 01:01:18,900
<font color="yellow">He didn't use the reports I gave him.</font>

999
01:01:18,900 --> 01:01:21,280
<font color="yellow">He didn't even ask any questions.</font>

1000
01:01:22,950 --> 01:01:24,180
<font color="yellow">The trial's over.</font>

1001
01:01:24,910 --> 01:01:26,410
<font color="yellow">I'll take him to Supreme Court.</font>

1002
01:01:26,810 --> 01:01:27,880
<font color="yellow">Everything he did...</font>

1003
01:01:27,880 --> 01:01:29,950
<font color="yellow">Prosecution refused to appeal!</font>

1004
01:01:33,550 --> 01:01:34,580
<font color="yellow">That's the reality...</font>

1005
01:01:36,080 --> 01:01:37,410
<font color="yellow">of the legal system...</font>

1006
01:01:39,450 --> 01:01:40,980
<font color="yellow">we believed in.</font>

1007
01:01:44,180 --> 01:01:45,180
<font color="yellow">I will...</font>

1008
01:01:46,650 --> 01:01:48,810
<font color="yellow">judge Il Jae myself.</font>

1009
01:01:51,680 --> 01:01:53,680
<font color="yellow">I can do better than this.</font>

1010
01:02:29,180 --> 01:02:30,310
<font color="yellow">I, Hwang Jae Man,</font>

1011
01:02:30,910 --> 01:02:34,680
<font color="yellow">will run for presidency of the Republic of Korea.</font>

1012
01:02:35,450 --> 01:02:37,610
<font color="yellow">This is my promise to you.</font>

1013
01:02:38,550 --> 01:02:39,680
<font color="yellow">Justice.</font>

1014
01:02:40,450 --> 01:02:43,410
<font color="yellow">A society in which justice prevails.</font>

1015
01:02:43,880 --> 01:02:45,180
<font color="yellow">As of today,</font>

1016
01:02:46,180 --> 01:02:47,950
<font color="yellow">I declare war against...</font>

1017
01:02:48,450 --> 01:02:51,610
<font color="yellow">corruption and all things illegal!</font>

1018
01:03:06,750 --> 01:03:07,750
<font color="yellow">I am...</font>

1019
01:03:08,250 --> 01:03:10,610
<font color="yellow">finally back, Guk Cheol.</font>

1020
01:03:38,010 --> 01:03:40,150
<font color="yellow">(Monster)</font>

1021
01:03:40,150 --> 01:03:41,440
<font color="yellow">He betrayed him?</font>

1022
01:03:41,440 --> 01:03:43,450
<font color="yellow">He'll be willing to meet me at least.</font>

1023
01:03:43,450 --> 01:03:46,080
<font color="yellow">It's worth the try if we get the timing right.</font>

1024
01:03:46,080 --> 01:03:47,910
<font color="yellow">You must stick to me.</font>

1025
01:03:47,910 --> 01:03:51,220
<font color="yellow">Did you have anything to do with Gwang Woo killing Gi Tan's parents?</font>

1026
01:03:51,220 --> 01:03:54,050
<font color="yellow">I think we should let Dad go.</font>

1027
01:03:54,050 --> 01:03:56,310
<font color="yellow">You stand a chance if we help you.</font>

1028
01:03:56,310 --> 01:03:58,310
<font color="yellow">Are you suggesting we join forces?</font>

1029
01:03:58,310 --> 01:03:59,400
<font color="yellow">It's about what happens next.</font>

1030
01:03:59,400 --> 01:04:01,750
<font color="yellow">This is Kang Gi Tan. Could we meet?</font>

